trans-unit.source: The DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry class defines the smallest unit of a code access security permission set for <xref href="System.DirectoryServices"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry definierar den minsta enheten av en code access security behörighetsgrupp för <xref href="System.DirectoryServices"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry constructor initializes a new instance of the DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktorn DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry initierar en ny instans av klassen DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry.

trans-unit.source: The path of the Active Directory Domain Services node to which the permissions apply.
trans-unit.target: Sökvägen till den Active Directory Domain Services-noden som behörigheterna som gäller.

trans-unit.source: The Path property gets a path to an Active Directory Domain Services node to which the permissions apply.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Path hämtar en sökväg till en Active Directory Domain Services-nod som behörigheterna som gäller.

trans-unit.source: The path to an Active Directory Domain Services node.
trans-unit.target: Sökvägen till en Active Directory Domain Services-nod.

trans-unit.source: The PermissionAccess property gets the access levels used in creating permissions.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen PermissionAccess hämtar åtkomstnivåer som används för att skapa behörigheter.
